'''一氧化二硼'''（[[化学式|化学式]]：B<sub>2</sub>O）是由[[硼|硼]]和[[氧|氧]]形成的一种[[化合物|化合物]]。两篇实验研究已经分别指出了具有[[钻石|钻石]]结构<ref>
{{cite journal
 |last1=Endo |first1=T.
 |last2=Sato |first2=T.
 |last3=Shimada |first3=M.
 |year=1987
 |title=High-pressure synthesis of B<sub>2</sub>O with diamond-like structure
 |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-materials-science-letters_1987-06_6_6/page/683 |journal=[[Journal_of_Materials_Science_Letters|Journal of Materials Science Letters]]
 |volume=6 |issue=6 |pages=683
 |doi=10.1007/BF01770925
}}</ref>和[[石墨|石墨]]结构<ref>
{{cite journal
 |last1   = Hall
 |first1  = H. T.
 |last2   = Compton
 |first2  = L. A.
 |year    = 1965
 |title   = Group IV Analogs and High Pressure, High Temperature Synthesis of B<sub>2</sub>O
 |url     = http://67.50.46.175/pdf/19650231.pdf
 |journal = [[Inorganic_Chemistry_(journal)|Inorganic Chemistry]]
 |volume  = 4
 |issue   = 8
 |pages   = 1213
 |doi     = 10.1021/ic50030a027
}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>的B<sub>2</sub>O的存在，这正如[[氮化硼|氮化硼]]和[[碳|碳]]固体的两种存在形式。然而，随后的一个对硼-氧[[相图|相图]]的系统性研究暗示称B<sub>2</sub>O实际上是不稳定的。<ref>
